---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-100 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
      <!-- Back link -->
      <a href="/structural-burnout" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-teal-400 hover:text-teal-300 mb-10 text-sm">
        ← Back to Structural Burnout
      </a>

      <!-- Hero -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div class="inline-block px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-zinc-900 border border-teal-400/30 text-teal-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8">
          Executive Pitch • UNMASK
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tighter leading-none mb-8">
          Your Organization Is Not Burned Out.<br/>
          <span class="text-teal-400">It Is Architecturally Strained.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Burnout is not a personal failure of resilience. It is a smoke alarm signaling that your leadership architecture was never designed for the speed of AI.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Thesis Cards -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-20">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-red-500/30 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:border-red-400/50 transition">
          <div class="text-red-400 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">The Problem</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Structural Friction Is the Real Crisis</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400">When responsibility exceeds authority, load accumulates in the middle layer until something gives. It is always your best people who absorb the most pressure.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-teal-400/30 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:border-teal-400/50 transition">
          <div class="text-teal-400 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">The Accelerant</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">AI Multiplies Whatever Exists</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400">AI does not fix a strained bridge. It puts 10× more traffic on it. Organizations deploying AI onto misaligned architecture are accelerating capacity loss.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-blue-400/30 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:border-blue-400/50 transition">
          <div class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">The Solution</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Recalibration Is a Fiduciary Duty</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400">The UNMASK Engine identifies exactly where your structure is leaking capacity and gives leaders the authority architecture to correct it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-20">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900 border-l-4 border-teal-400 p-8 rounded-3xl">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-2">213%</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-500">Replacement Cost per Leader</div>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-4 text-sm">The true cost of losing a mid-to-senior leader to structural burnout.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-900 border-l-4 border-teal-400 p-8 rounded-3xl">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-2">30%</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-500">Authority Gap</div>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-4 text-sm">Leaders carry 100% responsibility but only ~30% decision authority. That gap is where your payroll leaks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Investor Seed Capital Section (as requested) -->
      <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-teal-400/20 rounded-3xl p-12 mb-20">
        <div class="text-center mb-10">
          <div class="inline-block px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-teal-400/10 text-teal-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Investor Briefing</div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tighter mt-6 mb-4">Seed Capital for the UNMASK Engine</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 max-w-md mx-auto">Transitioning from consultancy to a data-native diagnostic platform standard.</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-center text-zinc-400 mb-10">We are seeking <strong class="text-white">$30,000</strong> in seed velocity to build the AI Audit Agent and proprietary scoring algorithms.</p>
        <div class="text-center">
          <a href="#" class="inline-block px-10 py-5 bg-teal-400 hover:bg-teal-300 text-zinc-950 font-bold rounded-2xl transition">
            View Full Investor Deck →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">"Stop managing people. Start protecting capacity."</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-10 max-w-md mx-auto">Book a direct conversation or start the Structural Audit.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="https://calendar.google.com/appointments/schedules/AcZssZ0wzeoxprLGxanzVAEMZB_aBMMuQycSnCwYHy3gsd1R3wpmUCMIHmegk-UbZzU2nRZb_XiI_I3o" 
             target="_blank"
             class="px-10 py-5 bg-teal-400 hover:bg-teal-300 text-zinc-950 font-bold rounded-2xl transition">
            Book a Call
          </a>
          <a href="/structural-burnout/services" 
             class="px-10 py-5 border border-zinc-700 hover:border-teal-400 text-white font-bold rounded-2xl transition">
            Explore Full Solutions
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>